### Obtener todos los menús
GET http://localhost:8080/menus
Content-Type: application/json


###

### Crear un nuevo menú
POST http://localhost:8080/menus
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pizza Margarita",
  "price": 9.99,
  "content": "Queso, tomate, albahaca",
  "active": true,
  "waiter": false
}

###

### Obtener todas las órdenes
GET http://localhost:8080/orders
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Crear orden EatIn
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/eatin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "table_id": 1,
  "menu_ids": [1, 3]
}

###

### Crear orden Takeaway
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/takeaway
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pickup_time": "2025-07-20T18:00:00Z",
  "menu_ids": [1, 2, 3]
}

###

### Crear orden Shipping
POST http://localhost:8080/orders/shipping
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "Av. Amazonas 123",
  "phone_number": "0991234567",
  "status": "Pendiente",
  "menu_ids": [1, 4]
}


###

### Eliminar un menu
DELETE http://localhost:8080/menus/2
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Eliminar una orden
DELETE http://localhost:8080/orders/3
Content-Type: application/json